title: Fastest - WeStyle Fashion - Main Area - Advertisement
content:
Complete Perfect Set for your house

The Beetle Sofa invites conversation. Taking its inspiration from the Beetle Lounge Chair, the elongated Beetle Sofa plays with the contrast between the enveloping outer shell and a soft and inviting interior.

A bling pair of sandals is the corner stone of any girls outfit this season. Though high, the chunky platform and adjustable strap ensure a steady stride. Complement yours with darker tones.
